      "title": "14 people have voted for Ranil",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Member of Parliament Harin Fernando said that 14 MPs representing Samagi Jana Balawega have voted for the appointment of Mr. Ranil Wickramasinghe as President.",
        "Mr. Harin Fernando said that out of those 14 MPs, six represent the Sinhalese community and the remaining eight represent the Tamil and Muslim communities."
